{"SOS":[{"def":"The letters signified by the signal ( .","pos":""}],"SOSS":[{"def":"To fall at once into a chair or seat; to sit lazily.","pos":""}],"SOSTENUTO":[{"def":"Sustained; -- applied to a movement or passage the sounds of which are to sustained to the utmost of the nominal value of the time; also, to a passage the tones of which are to be somewhat prolonged or protacted.","pos":""}]}